image_analysis.description: This is an image of a completed OGE Form 278e, Part 2, titled 'Filer's Employment Assets and Income'. The form lists various assets, their value, and the income they generate. The filer's name is identified as Donald J. Trump. The document is page 14 of 51 and has a Bates number 'HOUSE_OVERSIGHT_010630' at the bottom right.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header section with the form title, filer's name, and page number. The main body is a table with seven columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'attached schedule (Part 2 - EXHIBIT A) Reference #', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. Below the table, there is a footer with a note about an accompanying schedule.
